o%20see%20top%20earners%20pay%20a%20higher%20tax%20rate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELaLota%20said%20Saturday%20that%20the%20idea%20would%20help%20push%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%20bill%26quot%3B%20forward.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20GOP-led%20tax%20and%20immigration%20package%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20passes%20%E2%80%94%20could%20define%20Trump's%20second%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20GOP%20congressman%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20raising%20the%20top%20tax%20rate%20for%20high%20earners%20could%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20massive%20tax%20and%20immigration%20package%20get%20the%20votes%20it%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-beautiful-bill-medicaid-taxes-maga-accounts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOne%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20stalled%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20needs%20wind%20in%20its%20sails%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Nick%20LaLota%20said%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BAllowing%20the%20top%20tax%20rate%20to%20expire%20%E2%80%94%20returning%20from%2037%25%20to%2039.6%25%20for%20individuals%20earning%20over%20%24609%2C350%20and%20married%20couples%20earning%20over%20%24731%2C200%20%E2%80%94%20breathes%20%24300%20billion%20of%20new%20life%20into%20the%20effort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaLota%20said%20that%20his%20proposal%20would%20be%20fiscally%20prudent%20and%20could%20be%20done%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20raising%20taxes%20on%20the%20middle%20class.%26quot%3B%20The%20New%20York%20congressman%20has%20suggested%20that%20the%20money%20generated%20from%20raising%20taxes%20on%20high%20earners%20could%20protect%20Medicaid%20and%20%26quot%3Bfix%26quot%3B%20the%20cap%20on%20the%20so-called%20SALT%20deduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20SALT%20deduction%20allows%20taxpayers%20to%20deduct%20their%20state%20and%20local%20tax%20payments.%20Since%202018%2C%20however%2C%20