ecided%20she%20loved%20mushrooms%2C%20radishes%2C%20or%20spinach%20(which%2C%20to%20be%20fair%2C%20she%20had%20mistaken%20for%20basil).%20But%20that%20didn't%20mean%20it%20was%20easy.%20I%20am%20constantly%20aware%20of%20the%20tables%20around%20us%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20aren't%20disrupting%20anyone's%20dinner%20or%20the%20people%20working%20in%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202dfaad8-a897-489a-82a5-4dfe5128cdc9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20bring%20stuff%20to%20keep%20her%20entertained%2C%20just%20in%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20a%202-year-old%20is%20a%20well-mannered%20foodie%2C%20they%20are%20still%20unpredictable.%20However%2C%20I've%20found%20we%20have%20the%20best%20luck%20when%20I%20make%20the%20reservation%20for%20a%205%20p.m.%20early%20dinner%20before%20Via%20gets%20too%20tired%20%E2%80%94%20and%20while%20the%20restaurant%20ambiance%20is%20slightly%20more%20casual.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feed%20her%20a%20snack%20before%20we%20leave%20for%20the%20restaurant%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20bring%20any%20with%20me%20to%20ensure%20she's%20hungry%20enough%20to%20try%20the%20food%20when%20it%20arrives.%20Since%20many%20of%20these%20restaurants%20have%20beautiful%20table%20settings%2C%20I%20play%20it%20safe%20by%20bringing%20%3Cspan%3Ea%20small%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0d6808d4aec6dae8afc04b4bcb27ef6042a0bcb06b1049d007c828d1f0413d02%26postID%3D680004ee3d37c2e3ad492b48%26postSlug%3Dhow-restaurant-reviewer-takes-her-toddler-for-fine-dining-meals-2025-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fezpzfun.com%252Fproducts%252Fmini-mat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuction%20placemat%2Fplate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0for%20my%20daughter%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20a%20plastic%20bag%20to%20bring%20it%20home%20once%20it's%20used.%20I%20also%20keep%20an%20emergency%20stash%20of%20no-mess%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi