%20was%20done%20having%20kids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20First%2C%20we%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20and%20then%20our%20son%20joined%20the%20mix%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20two%20was%20enough.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20as%20any%20parenting%20story%20goes%2C%20things%20didn't%20turn%20out%20like%20I%20planned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20myself%20nesting%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20traded%20a%20crib%20for%20a%20desk.%20When%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-ireland-when-fifteen-was-treated-like-an-adult-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprepared%20for%20my%20teenage%20nephew's%20arrival%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20envisioned%20him%20hunched%20over%20the%20wooden%20table%2C%20cramming%20for%20a%20calculus%20test%20or%20writing%20his%20college%20entrance%20essays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20vision%20actually%20did%20come%20true%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20studious%20and%20had%20a%20pretty%20steady%20head%20on%20his%20shoulders%20when%20he%20arrived%20on%20our%20doorstep.%20But%20much%20of%20what%20I%20had%20planned%20for%20him%20was%20different%20from%20the%20detailed%20picture%20I%20had%20painted%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296d99a1a-af36-4ce8-9725-4ae0ad5b5189%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20potty%20training%20and%20raising%20a%20teen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%2015-year-old%20nephew%20moved%20in%20with%20us%20in%202020%2C%20although%20I%20didn't%20know%20it%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20graced%20with%20the%20gift%20of%20ignorance.%20I%20was%20raising%20little%20ones%2C%206%20and%203%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fpotty-training%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efully%20immersed%20in%20potty%20training%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C