20had%20to%20go%20out%20and%20make%20mistakes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f617b276-2508-4c9e-89d1-2763136e8554%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20clear%20boundaries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20to%20realize%20that%20much%20of%20that%20foundation%20built%20in%20his%20earlier%20years%20is%20already%20there.%20I%20can't%20change%20what%20happened%20in%20his%20past%2C%20but%20can%20I%20guide%20him%20on%20what%20to%20do%20with%20the%20cards%20he%20was%20dealt%3F%20It%20was%20about%20witnessing%20what%20he%20can%20do%20with%20it%2C%20without%20us.%20I%20learned%20to%20be%20there%20for%20when%20the%20bones%20and%20drywall%20are%20nailed%20in%2C%20and%20let%20him%20decide%20where%20everything%20goes%2C%20with%20smart%20boundaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20often%20bounced%20between%20stern%20and%20serious%20or%20goofy%20auntie%20but%20I%20always%20made%20it%20a%20priority%20to%20make%20boundaries%20clear%20because%20I%20learned%20that%20these%20child%20minds%20in%20adult%20bodies%20need%20them%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20pissed%20at%20you%20for%20making%20them%20in%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20it%20was%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20look%20at%20it%20that%20way%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20he%20was%20not%20my%20son%2C%20we%20did%20not%20start%20together%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20in%20those%20messy%2C%20hands-on%20days.%20Some%20can%20say%20I%20wasn't%20as%20invested%2C%20but%20maybe%20that's%20what%20worked%20for%20us.%20I%20could%20better%20remove%20that%20layer%20of%20overprotection%20mode%2C%20I%20feel%2C%20when%20I'm%20with%20my%20own%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ccd00a5-7a22-4918-935e-60f90ac295c8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20tried%20to%20remember%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20be%20a%20teen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20he%20wasn't%20my%20son%2C%20I%20could%20change%20gears%20more%20easily.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20risk%20taker%2C