ely%20advanced%20mission%20equipment%20package%20that%20allows%20it%20to%20spot%20dangers%20and%20targets%2C%20threats%20and%20targets.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that's%20the%20real%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAboulafia%20said%20that%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flockheed-martin-fighter-aircraft-turbulence-trump-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elow-observable%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20that%20there%20is%20less%20of%20a%20risk%20of%20being%20spotted%20and%20tracked%2C%20not%20that%20the%20plane%20is%20entirely%20stealthy%20all%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20a%20jet%20is%20employed%2C%20such%20as%20if%20munitions%20are%20carried%20externally%20in%20what%20has%20been%20described%20for%20F-35s%20as%20%26quot%3Bbeast%20mode%2C%26quot%3B%20can%20compromise%20stealth.%20Adversary%20air%20defenses%20can%20turn%20on%20their%20system%20at%20the%20right%20place%20at%20the%20right%20time%20and%20get%20lucky%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20recent%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20US%20F-35%20avoided%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthi-missile-israel-air-defense-system-iran-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHouthi%20missile%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20jet%20was%20actually%20targeted%20or%20if%20the%20rebels%20just%20fired%20in%20that%20general%20direction%20and%20happened%20to%20get%20somewhat%20close%20to%20the%20aircraft%2C%20forcing%20evasive%20maneuvers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouthi%20air%20defenses%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20threat%20to%20military%20and%20civilian%20aircraft%20and%20platforms%20operating%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Yemen%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%20Davis%2C%20a%20retired%20US%20Army%20major%20general%20and%20NATO's%20former%20deputy%20assistant%20secretary-general%20for%20its%20Defense%20Investment%20Division%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20team%