%20in%20Bagalkot%20district%2C%20Karnataka.%20Here%2C%20hand-spun%20and%20hand-woven%20cotton%20khadi%20cloth%20is%20made%20with%20precision%20and%20patience.%20The%20fabric%20then%20travels%20to%20the%20KKGSS%20unit%20in%20Bengeri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20entirely%20manual.%20No%20fancy%20machines%20or%20shortcuts.%20The%20cloth%20is%20dyed%20saffron%2C%20white%2C%20and%20green%20in%20three%20separate%20lots%2C%20representing%20courage%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20faith%2C%20respectively.%20The%20navy-blue%20Ashoka%20Chakra%20with%2024%20spokes%20is%20carefully%20printed%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20white%20section.%20Stitching%20together%20the%20three%20panels%20into%20one%20seamless%20flag%20is%20a%20skill%20honed%20by%20years%20of%20practice.%20Once%20stitched%2C%20the%20flags%20are%20ironed%2C%20inspected%2C%20and%20packed%20for%20dispatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20national%20flag%2C%20KKGSS%20also%20produces%20other%20khadi%20products%2C%20such%20as%20clothes%2C%20carpets%2C%20bags%2C%20caps%2C%20bed%20sheets%2C%20soaps%2C%20hand-made%20paper%2C%20and%20processed%20honey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPerfection%20is%20patriotic%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20KKGSS%2C%20making%20the%20national%20flag%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20task%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20responsibility%20carried%20with%20deep%20reverence.%20Every%20tricolour%20that%20leaves%20the%20workshop%20must%20meet%20the%20exact%20specifications%20laid%20out%20by%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standards%20(BIS)%20and%20the%20Flag%20Code%20of%20India.%20From%20the%20thread%20count%20in%20the%20khadi%20to%20the%20precise%20shade%20of%20saffron%2C%20from%20the%20hand-dyed%20Ashoka%20Chakra%20to%20the%20method%20of%20stitching%20%E2%80%94%20nothing%20is%20left%20to%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20millimetre%20off%2C%20and%20the%20flag%20is%20rejected.%20Because%20here%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20getting%20the%20details%20right%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20upholding%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20symbol%20millions%20salute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20flag%20is%20made%20in%20one%20of%20nine%20standard%20sizes%2C%20from%20palm-sized%20to%20monumental%2C%20depending%20on%20official%20use.%20Any%20variation%20beyond%20what%E2%80%99s%20permitted%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20flaw%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20legal%20violation%2C%20punishable%20by%20law.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20weight%20and%20pride%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20being%20made%20here%20%E2%80%94%20one%20stitch%2C%20one%20stripe%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fshutterstock_1480212536_11zon-1747384699-500x347.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Indian%20national%20flag%20must%20be%20made%20from%20cotton%2C%20silk%2C%20or%20wool%20khadi%2C%20but%20polyester%20and%20other%20synthetic%20materials%20are%20strictly%20prohibited.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20amended%20the%20Flag%20Code%20to%20allow%20machine-made%20flags%20using%20polyester%2C%20sparking%20debate%20and%20concern%20among%20traditional%20khadi%20flag%20makers%20like%20KKGSS%2C%20who%20uphold%20the%20hand-spun%20heritage%20of%20the%20original%20flag%20design.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi